=80=89965 =E2=80=93 c.=E2=80=891040) was the first to formulate <a href=3D"=
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wilson%27s_theorem" title=3D"Wilson's theorem=
">Wilson's theorem</a> connecting the factorials with the <a href=3D"https:=
